snippet.title: Castaway Paradise - Console Announcement Trailer I PS4, Xbox One
snippet.description:
www.CastawayParadiseGame.com

Town building sim Castaway Paradise is coming to consoles this July 31! Animal Crossing fans take note! Washed up on an idyllic tropical island, you are free to explore, go fishing, plant a garden, decorate your house, dress up with hundreds of different items, and more!

Pre-order the game now on PlayStation 4 or Xbox One and get a discount!
